   "body" : "Remove globals: Avoid using the global namespace if possible.\r\n\r\nPartially resolves #15612 (\"Reduce the number of globals used\").\r\n\r\nChange in globals as reported by `nm bitcoind` before vs after:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ diff -u <(nm src/bitcoind-before | c++filt | grep -E '^[0-9a-f]+ [A-Z] ' | cut -f3- -d' ' | sort -u) \\\r\n          <(nm src/bitcoind-after  | c++filt | grep -E '^[0-9a-f]+ [A-Z] ' | cut -f3- -d' ' | sort -u) \\\r\n          | grep -E '^[+-][^+-]'\r\n-boundSockets\r\n-cs_warnings\r\n-eventHTTP\r\n-fFeeEstimatesInitialized\r\n-fLargeWorkForkFound\r\n-fLargeWorkInvalidChainFound\r\n-pathHandlers\r\n-strMiscWarning[abi:cxx11]\r\n-threadHTTP\r\n```",
